Hello,

I am trying to modify an existing Excel-file containing a macro. 

The first step runs without any problems. I could read the Excel-file and read 
or modify individual cells. 

But when I am trying to write back the file, I become a NullPointerException.

//read excel
POIFSFileSystem fs = new POIFSFileSystem(new FileInputStream(args[0]));
HSSFWorkbook wb = new HSSFWorkbook(fs);
//modify
//...

//write excel
FileOutputStream stream = new FileOutputStream(args[1]);
wb.write(stream);//throws NullPointerException
stream.close();

(it is not possible to attach the Excel-file containing the macro)


Kind regards,

Mose
